So happy to share probably the most important and special moment of our entire lives.. I hope you guys enjoyed being able to watch. I look forward to looking back on this video a few years from now.
WARNING, this video WILL have you crying.

We also shared some personal information with you guys and why this baby is so much more meaningful to us.
This baby literally saved both of our lives and it was something we didn't know we needed.

We'll see you all again soon! With a school skit 🤪

Thank you for being apart of this new journey and chapter in our lives and we'll definitely keep you updated!

In the meantime, if you'd like more updates then DEFINITELY follow us on Instagram!
www.instagram.com/chillyjimenez
www.instagram.com/loganthirtyacre
www.instagram.com/titototters

And I'm also the only one in the SML crew to constantly update my Twitter so follow that if you use Twitter as well!
www.twitter.com/jimenezchilly

Love you guys!
oh and don't forget to sub Tito's channel (he's almost to one MILLION)
